'''Bahawalani''' is a sub-division of the [[Abro]] tribe. Bahawalani are descendents of Bahawaldin Abro I, and are natives of [[Larkana]] city of the [[Sindh]] province, Pakistan. {{citation needed|date=October 2017}}

== History ==
Bahawalani are Abro descendents of Jams of [[Samma Dynasty]] migrated from southern Sindh to the northern Sindh and are settled in Larkana city now.

