[[File:Aden Abdulle Osman Daar.jpg|thumb|Former leader of the [[Somali Youth League]] [[Aden Abdullah Osman Daar]] who eventually became the first President of the [[Somali Republic]] following the union of [[State of Somaliland]] and [[Italian Trusteeship of Somalia]].]]
