*[[Abdi Yusuf Hassan]] – Somali politician, diplomat and journalist. Former Director of [[IRIN]] and UNHCR Head of External and Media Relations in [[Southwest Asia|Southwest]] and [[Central Asia]].
[[File:Rageh Omaar.jpg|200px|thumb|Journalist [[Rageh Omaar]].]]
